  "Description": "\r\n  \r\n  Does DL Plus pacing feel just too slow for you? Well, introducing DL Blitz! A modified version of DL Plus which significantly reduces all wave intervals, as well as a few more pressuring features, forcing players to adapt a very fast playstyle.\r\n  \r\n  ET: \r\n  - Differences from DL Plus:\r\n    - Spawn cap at 4p increased to 200\r\n    - 50% more stationaries\r\n    - Increased enemy count modifier on certain mission phases & extraction\r\n    - Reduced the wave intervals for swarms, ambient waves & the common WS\r\n    - Mobile enemies with large HP scaling now gain stun & fear resistance, as well as increased temperature thresholds (these modifiers will scale later in the harder diffs)\r\n    - Oppressors move 1.25x faster\r\n    - Grunt WS -> Common WS, now has a chance to spawn web & acid spitters with grunts \r\n  \r\n  ",
